request.description:
Connect to private chat WebSocket. After connection, you can send these events:

**Send Private Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "send_private_message",
  "data": {
    "recipientId": "user-id-here",
    "content": "Hello from Postman!",
    "messageType": "TEXT"
  }
}
```

**Get Private Messages:**
```json
{
  "event": "get_private_messages",
  "data": {
    "recipientId": "user-id-here",
    "limit": 50
  }
}
```

**Edit Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "edit_message",
  "data": {
    "messageId": "message-id-here",
    "newContent": "Updated message content",
    "recipientId": "user-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Delete Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "delete_message",
  "data": {
    "messageId": "message-id-here",
    "recipientId": "user-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Mark Messages as Read:**
```json
{
  "event": "mark_messages_read",
  "data": {
    "messageIds": ["msg-id-1", "msg-id-2"],
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Typing Indicator:**
```json
{
  "event": "typing_private",
  "data": {
    "recipientId": "user-id-here",
    "isTyping": true
  }
}
```

**Get Online Status:**
```json
{
  "event": "get_online_status",
  "data": {
    "userIds": ["user-id-1", "user-id-2"]
  }
}
```

Connect to group chat WebSocket. After connection, you can send these events:

**Join Group:**
```json
{
  "event": "join_group",
  "data": {
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Send Group Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "send_group_message",
  "data": {
    "roomId": "room-id-here",
    "content": "Hello group from Postman!",
    "messageType": "TEXT"
  }
}
```

**Get Group Messages:**
```json
{
  "event": "get_group_messages",
  "data": {
    "roomId": "room-id-here",
    "limit": 50
  }
}
```

**Edit Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "edit_message",
  "data": {
    "messageId": "message-id-here",
    "newContent": "Updated message content",
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Delete Message:**
```json
{
  "event": "delete_message",
  "data": {
    "messageId": "message-id-here",
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Leave Group:**
```json
{
  "event": "leave_group",
  "data": {
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Mark Group Messages as Read:**
```json
{
  "event": "mark_group_messages_read",
  "data": {
    "messageIds": ["msg-id-1", "msg-id-2"],
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Get Group Members:**
```json
{
  "event": "get_group_members",
  "data": {
    "roomId": "room-id-here"
  }
}
```

**Get User Groups:**
```json
{
  "event": "get_user_groups",
  "data": {}
}
```
